{
    "rukus": [
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "The Smiter"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "What is the Smiter"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "And what makes you realize what the Smiter is"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "The Day (whereon) mankind will be like disseminated moths"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "And the mountains will be like carded wool tufts"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "Then, as for him whose scales weigh heavy, (i.e., with good deeds)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "So he will be in a satisfied livelihood"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "And, as for him whose scales weigh light, (i.e., with deeds)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "Then his home is the bottom of Hell (Literally: his mother is tumbling into Hell)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "And what makes you realize what it is"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "(It is) a Fire burning hot"
        }
    ]
}